basestation.bot.commands

Interface CommandCenter

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    FourWheelMovement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExtendedFourWheelMovement, MiniBotCommandCenter, ModbotCommandCenter

    public interface CommandCenter
    Class who's methods are all the commands that can be issued to a bot

    Each bot must implement this class with their own commands.

    If there are any important commands we believe all robots should have then place them here

    • Method Detail

      • sendKV

        boolean sendKV(java.lang.String key,
               java.lang.String value)
        Sends an arbitrary key and value over the associated bot's connection. Should only be used for quick prototyping, with the goal of creating a method wrapper around sending the KV.
        Parameters:
        key - A key to identify the type of command
        value - The value of the command
        Returns:
        True if the command seems to have sent correctly
